{"tid":490964,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"樓價癲升 施永青：不需要所有人都買得起","createTime":"2017-12-06T05:28:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-06T05:33:10.000Z","uid":153228,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"d948e2d5d272fdf623399bec61dd1a522d7191a3","tid":490964,"uid":153228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T05:28:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171206/large/1512531523_933e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171206%2Flarge%2F1512531523_933e.jpg&h=3062ee4c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n港樓價有升無跌，中原集團主席施永青在《am730》專欄撰文指，社會上很多人買不起樓，「但樓宇並不需要社會上所有人都買得起」。<br />\n<br />\n施永青以〈香港樓價 還可以再升嗎？〉為題，指香港是市場經濟，故政府不能實施限價政策，「只要買賣雙方你情我願，樓價升至甚麼水平，政府都不會左右」。他指在私人住宅市場，每年新供應為2萬個單位左右，但全港有250個家庭，只要有1%家庭買得起樓，就會供不應求。他又指若只容許用家買樓，必會破壞資本主義社會運作，「令擁有鈔票的價值大減，社會可能因而失去動力」。他又指若無投資者買樓收租，未有能力買樓人的人就無法解決居住問題。由於現時港樓價高企，他認為入市的投資者大都處於盈利狀態，故明年樓市仍由投資者主導，「樓價的升勢看來不易逆轉」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20171206/57546951\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171206%2F57546951&d=Wq1B2vxQIxiLuW1rWFbBrzPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=093ae39a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171206%2F57546951&h=b8fa5aac\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20171206/57546951</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 最好拿拿聲破頂，個泡沬加速爆"},{"pid":"478ef4e8e8138a711d71bc098911d2ba1c19e252","tid":490964,"uid":35430,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T05:33:10.000Z","msg":"我一直都撐樓價升到盡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}